Package: grossman
Title: Teaching Datasets for Econometrics
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Your", "Name", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A collection of cleaned datasets for teaching econometrics and applied
